00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,200
I can see the car now.

283
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,750
Follow that car and see where he goes.

284
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:29,310
Got it. Following now.

285
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,570
I can't see him right now.

286
00:18:46,570 --> 00:18:48,300
There's a bus blocking my view.

287
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:50,400
Bus...

288
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:56,600
[From Yitian Station
to Tianshan Road Intersection Station]

289
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:00,200
[Lianhua Village 1] [Lianhua Village 2]

290
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,190
[From Yitian Station
to Tianshan Road Intersection Station]

291
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:05,640
[Lianhua Village 3] [Dongsha Market]

292
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,130
[Dongsha Market Station]
[Zhangjia Road Station]

293
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,030
[Zhangjia Road]

294
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:08,350
[Haishou Island Pier Station]

295
00:19:09,670 --> 00:19:10,150
[Shilianhua Village]

296
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:13,550
[Laoshi Station] [Chengnan Middle School]

297
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:16,710
[Hebai Community Station]

298
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:19,550
[Hebai Community]

299
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:25,110
Near Hebai Community.

300
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:30,530
Wu.

301
00:19:30,590 --> 00:19:31,200
Let's go.

302
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:33,200
Let's look around Hebai Community.

303
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:43,640
Wen.

304
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:45,310
Lu Ming.

305
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,970
Why is he taking so long to eat?

306
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:10,220
He shook off Ren Yi, circled half the city

307
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:12,110
just to come back here for a meal?

308
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:15,790
Are you sure he's here to eat?

309
00:20:17,810 --> 00:20:19,140
Eating isn't the point.

310
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:20,990
Wait a little longer.

311
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:29,920
[Old Kang Rice Noodle Shop]

312
00:20:32,470 --> 00:20:33,070
Lu Ming!

313
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:37,990
Officer Qin, Officer Wu.

314
00:20:38,510 --> 00:20:39,710
What brings you here?

315
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:40,350
By the way,

316
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:42,440
the porridge here is really good.

317
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,900
Drove halfway across the city
just to eat it?

318
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,310
How did you know?

319
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,080
Did you drive around too?

320
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,790
Now that you've had your fill,

321
00:20:51,790 --> 00:20:53,520
we have a few questions for you.

322
00:20:53,550 --> 00:20:53,920
Ask.

323
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:57,010
Why were you looking for Wang Bingkun?

324
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:59,550
Wang Bingkun owes us money.

325
00:20:59,550 --> 00:21:00,880
I was collecting a debt.

326
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,640
How much does he owe you

327
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:04,840
for you to go to such lengths to find him?

328
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:06,920
Well...

329
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:10,120
We have our own methods.

330
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,120
What about Ma Derong?

331
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:16,750
Ma Derong?

332
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:25,480
You mean Ma Derong from the shipyard?

333
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:27,030
Isn't he in prison?

334
00:21:27,030 --> 00:21:28,830
Lu Ming, don't play dumb with us.

335
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,890
No, I'm cooperating, aren't I?

336
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:34,310
Then we thank you for your cooperation.

337
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:35,680
Any more questions?

338
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:36,810
If not, I'm leaving.

339
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,510
Wen, are we just letting him go?

340
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:47,000
Keep following him.

341
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,660
Be careful.

342
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,400
Yes.

343
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:48,960
Go now.

344
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:02,670
Hello?

345
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,200
I'm sorry, Mr. Ma.

346
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,640
Something happened.

347
00:22:14,420 --> 00:22:20,670
[One day ago]

348
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,830
Take care.

349
00:22:40,830 --> 00:22:41,720
Come early tomorrow.

350
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:42,400
Okay.

351
00:22:42,790 --> 00:22:43,550
Drive safe.

352
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:44,240
Okay.

353
00:22:45,410 --> 00:22:47,270
Old Kang, closing up so early?

354
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,790
I miss my grandson.

355
00:22:48,790 --> 00:22:50,520
I'm going home to play with him.

356
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:51,920
Alright, I'm off.

357
00:22:52,110 --> 00:22:52,480
Work's done.

358
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:52,830
Okay.

359
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:05,890
Xiaohu.

360
00:23:06,830 --> 00:23:07,460
Grandpa.

361
00:23:07,550 --> 00:23:08,920
It's so late, you're still not going home?

362
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,250
Still playing outside?

363
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,900
Come on, go home with Grandpa.

364
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,640
Let's go!

365
00:23:17,850 --> 00:23:18,550
Old Kang!

366
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,440
Bought treats for your grandson again?

367
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,310
He loves them.

368
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:22,910
I'll just fix them up at home.

369
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:24,790
Take care.

370
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:27,000
Okay.

371
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:55,510
What's your name?

372
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:56,830
Kang Xiaohu.

373
00:23:59,770 --> 00:24:02,430
Your grandpa runs
Kang's Porridge Shop, right?

374
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:07,830
Chang, go back to the office first.

375
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:09,840
[Wear a helmet when cycling,
get home safely]

376
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,900
Be careful not to give anything away.

377
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:17,440
Where is Lu Ming?

378
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,070
Please, he's the boss.

379
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,420
I'm just an employee.

380
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,000
Chang,

381
00:24:22,090 --> 00:24:24,020
go to the bus stop on Zhangjia Road.

382
00:24:24,210 --> 00:24:25,270
I can't see him right now.

383
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:26,690
There's a bus blocking my view.

384
00:24:26,690 --> 00:24:27,690
You've probably been spotted.

385
00:24:27,690 --> 00:24:28,160
[Hebai Community]

386
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:28,740
That probably isn't Lu Ming
in the car either.

387
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:30,260
[Hebai Community Station]

388
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:45,010
Boss, enjoy your meal.

389
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,140
Don't move.

390
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:52,580
If you want to know
where your grandson is, sit down.

391
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,690
Don't move.

392
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,170
Sit down.

393
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:08,550
Wen.

394
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:18,680
What do you want?

395
00:25:19,790 --> 00:25:21,920
Where did Ma Derong hide Hou Shanshan?

396
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:24,270
What Shanshan?

397
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:26,000
I don't know.

398
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,800
Ma Derong was in for 10 years.

399
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:33,020
You visited him a lot, didn't you?

400
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:37,510
Calling you his most trusted person,

401
00:25:37,510 --> 00:25:39,570
wouldn't be an exaggeration, right?

402
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:42,650
How about this.

403
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,310
Let's make a deal.

404
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:47,240
You tell me where Hou Shanshan is hidden,

405
00:25:48,270 --> 00:25:50,530
and I'll tell you where your grandson is.

406
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:57,440
Things run a certain way on the streets.

407
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,800
I'll give you 20 seconds.

408
00:26:21,110 --> 00:26:22,990
Why hasn't he finished eating yet?

409
00:26:22,990 --> 00:26:24,320
Eating isn't the point.

410
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,080
Wait a little longer.

411
00:26:44,070 --> 00:26:44,680
Chang.

412
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,400
I'll talk.

413
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:49,200
I'll talk.

414
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:55,080
Xia Xue.

415
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:56,950
We've located Shanshan.

416
00:26:57,190 --> 00:26:58,990
Go to Shatang Village right now.

417
00:26:59,240 --> 00:27:01,350
The police are already onto Ma Derong.

418
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,480
We need to hurry.

419
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,400
Shanshan.

420
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,350
Shanshan.

421
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:20,750
Shanshan.

422
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:21,550
Mom!

423
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,400
Mom.

424
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:37,270
Mom, I missed you so much.

425
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:39,960
It's okay. Mom's here.

426
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:41,000
Mom's here.

427
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,290
Hello, Lu Ming.

428
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:50,480
I found Shanshan.

429
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,920
She's fine.

430
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:54,110
But I don't see Ma Derong here.

431
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,240
That's great.

432
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:58,750
Stay safe.

433
00:27:59,240 --> 00:27:59,830
Yeah.

434
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:09,400
Lin Hua, Shanshan's been found.

435
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,850
How is it on your end?

436
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:13,830
Ma Derong still hasn't shown up.

437
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:15,030
Keep watching.

438
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:16,590
There are police here.

439
00:28:16,590 --> 00:28:17,850
I can't go back for now.

440
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:19,600
Be careful.

441
00:28:19,620 --> 00:28:21,420
Ma Derong is bound to make a move.

442
00:28:22,250 --> 00:28:23,510
I'll keep an eye on him.

443
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:26,730
You protect yourself too.

444
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:27,960
Don't act rashly.

445
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,110
Okay. Wait for news.

446
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,400
Shanshan has been found.

447
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,170
Your grandson is home, too.

448
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:49,020
There are police at the door.

449
00:28:50,030 --> 00:28:51,760
If you don't want to get caught,

450
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,640
wait half an hour before going back.

451
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:04,720
Officer Qin, Officer Wu.
What brings you here?

452
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,030
Grandpa!

453
00:29:21,790 --> 00:29:22,640
Xiaohu!

454
00:29:59,000 --> 00:29:59,550
For you.

455
00:30:06,750 --> 00:30:07,810
Thank you, mister.

456
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:23,640
Hello?

457
00:30:23,830 --> 00:30:24,830
I'm sorry, Mr. Ma.

458
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:25,720
I'm sorry.

459
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,880
Lu Ming used Xiaohu to threaten me.

460
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:30,440
He forced me to reveal

461
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:32,110
Shanshan's hiding place.

462
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,550
I didn't know he was bluffing.

463
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,270
I was worried about Xiaohu's safety,

464
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:38,960
so I...

465
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,220
That's not important.

466
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:43,520
Who was the person behind Wang Bingkun?

467
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:45,100
I won't let go of the things

468
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,970
that need to be investigated.

469
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:08,520
Shanshan!

470
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,640
Let Dad take a look.

471
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,730
You're not hurt, right?

472
00:31:19,410 --> 00:31:20,510
Where did you find her?

473
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:21,400
I'll tell you when we get back.

474
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:22,030
Okay.

475
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:22,960
Shanshan, let's go home.

476
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:23,510
Mrs. Hou.

477
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,200
She's back.

478
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:26,310
You two, you two!

479
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:28,310
It's wonderful. My child is back!

480
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:29,750
Don't mention it.
I'm just glad she's been found.

481
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:30,750
She's been found.

482
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:31,790
Why don't we all go inside?

483
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:33,110
Let’s go in.
No.

484
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:35,880
Mrs. Hou, please come
to the Criminal Investigation Unit

485
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,340
to make a statement, okay?

486
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,160
Now?

487
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:39,070
Yes.

488
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:40,550
But the child just got back.

489
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,550
Look, she's been frightened.

490
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:42,640
Let her rest tonight.

491
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:44,200
We'll go first thing tomorrow, okay?

492
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:46,000
Mr. Hou, we understand how you feel.

493
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,750
After all, your child was just found.

494
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:50,110
But we hope you'll cooperate with us,

495
00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:51,080
alright?

496
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:52,590
Yes, we understand. We get it.

497
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:53,110
Of course we-

498
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:54,640
Let's listen to the police.

499
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:58,670
Okay. Alright then.

500
00:31:58,670 --> 00:32:00,550
[Police]

501
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:01,080
Let's go.

502
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:01,500
You're back.

503
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:03,440
[One-Stop Service Counter]

504
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,160
I'm sorry,

505
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:04,880
Mr. Hou, Mrs. Hou.

506
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,700
We made you come out when it's so late.

507
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:07,240
[Nanping Police Bureau]

508
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:08,370
I'll take them upstairs first.

509
00:32:08,370 --> 00:32:10,570
Could you please wait here for a moment?

510
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:12,480
Sure.

511
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:14,640
You go ahead.

512
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,410
I'll wait for you here.

513
00:32:15,410 --> 00:32:15,510
[One-Stop Service Counter]

514
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:16,310
Let's go upstairs first.

515
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:16,880
Okay.

516
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,080
Come here, Shanshan.

517
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,210
Come, let Mommy hold your hand.

518
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,310
Don't be afraid, Shanshan.

519
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,680
The reason auntie
asked you to come here today

520
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:30,160
is to ask you a few questions.

521
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,400
Just tell auntie whatever

522
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,920
you can remember, okay?

523
00:32:33,270 --> 00:32:34,960
Mommy is right here with you.

524
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,110
You are safe.

525
00:32:36,110 --> 00:32:38,310
You don't need to be afraid of anything.

526
00:32:38,550 --> 00:32:41,270
Let's start from the day you went out

527
00:32:41,270 --> 00:32:42,960
to walk Taotao,

528
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:43,720
okay?

529
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,310
That night,

530
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,640
I snuck out of the house.

531
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:52,380
Taotao!

532
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:55,800
I was taken by someone
and taken to a strange place.

533
00:32:59,400 --> 00:32:59,930
Who is it?

534
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,060
What are you doing?

535
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,110
So that Grandpa

536
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:03,240
just saved you from the bad guy,

537
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:05,160
and never hurt you at all,

538
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:05,720
right?

539
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:16,030
Shanshan, think carefully.

540
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:18,590
Any detail you remember, you must tell us.

541
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:20,340
That way we can catch the bad guys sooner.

542
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:22,250
But Grandpa isn't a bad person.

543
00:34:23,710 --> 00:34:24,310
Shanshan.

544
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:27,130
Don't be afraid.

545
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,449
I'm here to save you.

546
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,070
Don't be afraid. It's okay now.

547
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,659
It won't hurt anymore.

548
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:39,110
I'll take you somewhere safe.

549
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:41,510
Once we catch the bad guy,

550
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:45,110
we'll go home safely.

551
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,110
Okay?

552
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,150
Good girl.

553
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,110
Shanshan.

554
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:14,020
That's most of the questions, right?

555
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:14,920
So, Shanshan,

556
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:17,400
auntie's done asking questions for today.

557
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:18,110
Thank you.

558
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,910
You can go home with your mom now.

559
00:35:23,990 --> 00:35:25,120
Excuse me, Mrs. Hou.

560
00:35:25,440 --> 00:35:26,960
I just want to confirm something with you.

561
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:29,360
Was it Lu Ming
who helped you find Shanshan?

562
00:35:33,710 --> 00:35:34,110
Yes.

563
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:36,360
Then I may have more questions later

564
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:38,360
and may need to speak with you again.

565
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,030
Okay.

566
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,370
Let's go. Give me your hand.

567
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,280
[Forensic Evidence Laboratory]

568
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,760
You're out. Let's go.

569
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,590
Let's go home.

570
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:51,150
They said

571
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:54,460
they have a few more questions for me.

572
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:57,070
More questions?

573
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,450
Why did you ask Lu Ming
to help find your child?

574
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,260
I thought

575
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:16,640
he might know more people.

576
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:20,000
I was really desperate to find my child,

577
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,980
so I wanted to try everything.

578
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,440
Then have you considered

579
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:28,730
why Ma Derong would go save Hou Shanshan?

580
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:37,550
Because

581
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:44,510
Ma Ke is Shanshan's biological father.

582
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,960
So when you gave birth
at Nanping Bo'ai International Hospital,

583
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:54,010
it was arranged by Ma Derong.

584
00:36:56,110 --> 00:36:57,240
Who else could it be?

585
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:04,950
What about Wang Bingkun?

586
00:37:05,630 --> 00:37:06,760
And Wang Bingkun?

587
00:37:11,190 --> 00:37:12,150
I don't know him.

588
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:24,830
That's all for today's questions.

589
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:27,360
I'll contact you if there's anything else.

590
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:28,320
Thank you for your cooperation.
